<title>USA: IDX Systems in pact with Imperial Bank.</title>
<headline>IDX Systems in pact with Imperial Bank.</headline>
<dateline>BURLINGTON, Vt. 1997-01-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>IDX Systems Corp said on Thursday it signed an agreement with Imperial Bancorp unit Imperial Bank of California for providing credit card transaction processing services from the IDX desktop.</p>
<p>The agreement provides healthcare organizations an easy transition to credit card processing services, the company said. IDX said the service would help with the collection process, especially the self-pay receivables.</p>
<p>((New York newsdesk 212-859-16100)</p>
